article_title: State says lawsuit not needed to protect TennCare applicants

article_metadata.description: NASHVILLE -- An attorney for the state of Tennessee told a federal appeals court Thursday that a court order is not needed to protect TennCare applicants because they are no longer being left in indefinite limbo
